By EVT, 
\begin_inset Formula $\left\Vert f\left(x_{d}\right)\right\Vert \le C_{f}\triangleq\sup_{s\in\overline{B}_{\overline{x}_{d}}\left(\boldsymbol{0}_{n}\right)}\left(\left\Vert f\left(s\right)\right\Vert \right)$
