 & =\beta\dot{e}^{\top}K[\text{sgn}](e)-\dot{e}^{\top}\left(t\right)g\left(k_{1},\kappa_{d},\theta^{\ast},\widehat{\theta},t\right)-\lambda_{P}P\left(t\right)+k_{1}\left(\beta\left\Vert e\left(t\right)\right\Vert _{1}-e^{\top}g\left(k_{1},\kappa_{d},\theta^{\ast},\widehat{\theta},t\right)\right)\\
 & =\beta\dot{e}^{\top}K[\text{sgn}](e)-\dot{e}^{\top}\left(t\right)g\left(k_{1},\kappa_{d},\theta^{\ast},\widehat{\theta},t\right)-\lambda_{P}P\left(t\right)+k_{1}\beta e^{\top}K[\text{sgn}](e)-k_{1}e^{\top}g\left(k_{1},\kappa_{d},\theta^{\ast},\widehat{\theta},t\right)\\
