\zeta\left(t\right) & \triangleq K_{\text{RISE}}\left\Vert r_{1}\left(t\right)\right\Vert _{1}-r_{1}^{\top}\left(t\right)D\left(\kappa_{d},\theta^{\ast},\hat{\theta},t\right)\\
