\end_inset

NOTE: 
\begin_inset Formula $P\left(t_{0}\right)$
\end_inset

 must satisfy:
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
P\left(t_{0}\right) & =\zeta\left(t_{0}\right)\\
